1 - About
    -----

    вЂњProofcaseвЂќ is a collection of
    self-contained Rocq developments.
    Each component is designed to
    stand independently, typically as
    a formal companion to a paper,
    note, or conceptual construction.


2 - Style
    -----

    The formalizations prioritize
    clarity and minimality.
    Developments follow established
    practices and conventions.


